Diverging palette

Method 1: 1: use 2 complementary colors (eg. blue/red) from previously defined qulitative palette and let hcl_diverging function do the scaling 2: use 1 color and select second color in IWH 2a: using C and L space similar to the first color 2b: using default IWH settings

Method 2: 1: use 2 complementary colors (eg. blue/red) from previously defined qulitative palette and let scale logically 1a: using mean C and L from both colors as starting points 1b: using max C and min L from both colors as starting points
